123
00:07:08,340 --> 00:07:10,380
(she'll easily have feelings for me.)

124
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:16,180
Butler.

125
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:18,020
Butler!

126
00:07:19,780 --> 00:07:20,700
Your Highness,

127
00:07:20,700 --> 00:07:21,700
here I am.

128
00:07:22,140 --> 00:07:23,420
When I take a bath today,

129
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,710
do have Shen Juanjuan

130
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:28,180
wait on me personally.

131
00:07:29,100 --> 00:07:30,660
Miss Juanjuan,

132
00:07:30,660 --> 00:07:33,180
when you bathe His Highness,

133
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:35,220
be very careful.

134
00:07:35,220 --> 00:07:37,020
If you hurt him,

135
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,820
