136
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:42,860
Why didn't you say so at first? I quit.

137
00:07:43,500 --> 00:07:44,620
No way.

138
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:45,980
You begged me

139
00:07:45,980 --> 00:07:47,660
