143
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:58,580
Off you go.

144
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:02,460
(Now, I'm in a real dilemma.)

145
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:07,500
Your Highness,

146
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:09,780
I'm here to bathe you.

147
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:12,180
(It's the first time
that a woman bathes me.)

148
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:13,340
(I'm so embarrassed.)

149
