(It's the first time that I bathe a man.)

150
00:08:15,060 --> 00:08:16,140
(Such bad luck.)

151
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:19,990
- (Isn't it way too awkward?)
- (Isn't it way too awkward?)

152
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:23,420
- (To get back home,)
- (To get back home,)

153
00:08:23,820 --> 00:08:24,780
- (I'll just do it!)
- (I'll just do it!)

154
