(Where's the scar?)

155
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:02,100
(No scar?)

156
00:09:02,900 --> 00:09:04,060
(Is it under her dress?)

157
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:05,140
(Flirt.)

158
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:07,380
(If I didn't need to play innocent,)

159
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:09,300
(I would be unmanning you.)

160
00:09:11,580 --> 00:09:12,420
Ouch.

161
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:17,140
Mercy, Your Highness.

162
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:19,740
